&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4447&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/LATAM-MEDELLIN-EL-HERBARIO-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LATAM - MEDELLIN- EL HERBARIO- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;107&quot; height=&quot;50&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
In an industrial chic dining room with high ceilings and a floor to ceiling wine wall, Chef Rodrigo Isaza&rsquo;s dynamic menu at El Herbario focuses on herbs and vegetarian cuisine, yet has plenty of meat and seafood dishes to please a variety of palates. Attire is casually sophisticated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book by online &lt;a href=&quot;http://medellin.restorando.com.co/restaurante/herbario&quot;&gt;http://medellin.restorando.com.co/restaurante/herbario&lt;/a&gt; or contact El Herbario by phone at +57 4 311 2537 ext. 105&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy &ndash; As a courtesy El Herbario asks for 24 hour cancelation notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;El Herbario will only hold table 15 min after the reservation time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club Card for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection Culinary amenity of house-made preserves by Chef Rodrigo Isaza utilizing local organic ingredients and artisanal methods. Guests can select from 3 flavors: Coconut + Maracuya / Forest Fruits / Citron + Maracuya. One gift per table.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferred bookings based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating Diners Club International Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

